as an aside a simple spoken python example

function greet with parameters name
    let greeting be enchant with string Hello variable name
    print with greeting
close function

function factorial with parameters n
    if n is less than or equal to 1
        return 1
    close if
    literally return n * factorial(n - 1)
close function

as an aside main program
greet with string literal World
let result be factorial with 5
print with result
